item.title: About
item.description: Welcome to the ngin, the Next Generation Internet Research Lab at Tennessee Tech. Our research areas include Named Data Networking, Big Science data transfers, Networking for AR/VR applications, Vehicular networks, Data center networking, and more. You can find a list of the latest publications in the Publications page. The research projects are guided by Dr. Susmit Shannigrahi.
